messages.msgSnippet: Hi everyone... I m coming out of lurkdom to comment on this age-revealing thing :)  I m 25 and have been lurking on the unschooling.com list for a while, and
messages.messageBody:
Hi everyone... I'm coming out of lurkdom to comment on
this age-revealing thing :) I'm 25 and have been
lurking on the unschooling.com list for a while, and
immediately followed Sandra over here (sounds sneaky,
doesn't it?) when she left. I am learning SO much..
thank you all for sharing your ideas, successes and
problems with everyone! (Even those like me who don't
contribute, but just take everything in! Hmmm... I
hope I'm not coming across like some crazed
unschooling stalker!! LOL!!)

Anyway, I just wanted to say hi!
Love, Tori

=====
Tori Kirkby
Creative spirit and mom to Jade (3 1/2) and mystery baby due in 2 weeks
